high_descs: Turn right, go to the counter
Pick up the tomato on the counter
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right, go forward, turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the stove
Put the tomato on the counter to the left of the stove
Pick up the knife on the counter
Slice the tomato on the counter
Put the knife on the stove
Pick up a tomato slice
Move a bit to the right
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the tomato slice from the microwave
Move a bit to the left
Put the tomato slice on the counter
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, cook a slice of tomato

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter between the door and stool.
Pick up a tomato from the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter that is left of the stove.
Put the tomato on the counter, left of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Put the slice of tomato in the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the counter left of the stove.
Put the slice of tomato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of cooked tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and face the counter in front of you.
Take the tomato from the counter in front of you.
Take a left then turn right and face the stove on your right.
Place the tomato on the counter next to the stove in front of you.
Pick up the knife from the counter in front of you.
Slice the tomato on the counter in front of you.
Cut a tomato slice out from the counter in front of you.
Take a tomato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the microwave on top of the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave in front of you then take it out.
Face the counter by the stove in front of you.
Place the tomato slice on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm tomato slice on the counter.
